description: Aspose.Diagram is a class library for working with Microsoft Visio files. It allows developers to create new diagrams and work with VSD, VSS, VST, VSX, VTX, VDW and VDX files on ASP.NET web applications, web services and Windows applications. It allows you to open files and manipulate the elements of the diagram, from lines and fills, to more complex elements, and then export to VDX, VSX, VTX, XPS, HTML, image or PDF formats.
releaseNotes:
This release introduces the features, enhancements and bug fixes as detailed below:
	Features
DIAGRAM-33185 - [Image Rendering] Support pre-defined page sizes
DIAGRAM-33148 - [Shape] Ability to set shape order (bring to front, send to back etc.)

Enhancements
DIAGRAM-33151 - [PageSize] Unable to auto size page

Bugs
DIAGRAM-33187 - [PDF Rendering] Text is misplaced inside group shapes
DIAGRAM-33189 - [PDF Rendering] Shapes are not maintaining the rounded corners
DIAGRAM-33190 - [PDF Rendering] Output PDF cannot be read with Adobe Reader
DIAGRAM-31084 - [PDF and XPS rendering] Error in the output PDF and XPS
DIAGRAM-33167 - [ShapeProps] Unable to add new string properties
